Nanjo: In this town, weapons{nl}
are entirely for fighting{nl}
demons.{waitkey}{clearbox}So that's why there's no need{nl}
for police, is it.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: No matter how often I{nl}
come, I never get used to it.{nl}
Getting a big smile and "Are{nl}
you looking for weapons?"{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: The magazines here are{nl}
all old ones, aren't they.{nl}
They're all from about a{nl}
