Ayase: No way! Look at this{nl}
model! Nobody wears clothes{nl}
like this anymore...{waitkey}{clearbox}Huh? This magazine's old.{nl}
It's a whole year old!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: What's with this shop?{nl}
It's full of oddly old{nl}
magazines.{waitkey}{ret}

Young Man: A spot that used to{nl}
be a lovely flower field{nl}
suddenly turned into a forest.{waitkey}Are they running some kind of{nl}
greening campaign now?{waitkey}{ret}

Townsperson: A girl often{nl}
played in the flower field.{waitkey}{clearbox}But now it's a forest. I{nl}
wonder how she's doing.{waitkey}{clearbox}? {wait_fr:32}Whether she wore black?{wait_fr:48}{nl}
No, that girl was a cute one,{nl}
dressed all in white.{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: Eek!{wait_fr:32} That doesn't{nl}
open!{wait_fr:32} If you're shopping,{nl}
please come around to the{nl}
counter!{waitkey}{ret}
